.TH KINGPEPE-WALLET 1
.SH NAME
kingpepe-wallet \- offline KingPepe Core wallet utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kingpepe-wallet
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fICOMMAND\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B kingpepe-wallet
tool creates and inspects KingPepe Core wallet files without requiring a running
node.
.SH OPTIONS
Run
.B kingpepe-wallet -help
for the complete option list supported by this build.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kingpeped (1),
.BR kingpepe-cli (1)
